## Always Task Claude (token saver)

**Default every coding session.** Cursor = thin router. Heavy work → `Task` with Claude model.

| Do | Don't |
|----|-------|
| `Task` → `claude-opus-4-8-thinking-high` or `claude-sonnet-5-thinking-high` | Cursor re-implements large features alone |
| Short prompt + plan path + file list | Dump whole repo into Cursor context |
| Cursor verify, smoke, short status | Long Cursor analysis / rival redesign |

Opt out only: `normal cursor` · `you do it` · `cursor lead`.

Reinforces `08-claude-senior-listener.mdc`.

## BUR / Direct Book — new file when change is big

Scope: 7 products (`0189`, `0191`–`0196`). Prefer **new BUR/DB slice file** over large edits to shared PUL/legacy.

### Prefer new file when

- Shared blade / Vue / PHP would grow **large** or risk **breaking** `0121`–`0125`
- Format/layout differs (e.g. Policy No vs Policy & Endorsement No)
- New print/export/report path for Direct Book only
- Backend branch would otherwise sprawl inside a shared service method

### Where new files go

| Layer | Prefer |
|-------|--------|
| Vue | `…/Endorsement/Components/Burglary/*`, `…/Policy/Components/Burglary/*`, `…/Quotation/Components/Burglary/*` |
| JS | `resources/js/services/property_liability/burglary/` (short names — `05-pl-db-naming.mdc`) |
| PHP service | `app/Services/PL/Endorsement/Burglary.php` (or small helper next to it) — not fat legacy methods |
| PDF | `resources/views/pdf/**/pl/direct_book/*` (clone + adapt; shared blade keeps thin `isDirectBook` include only if ≲ few lines) |
| Export | DB-specific export class/helper under `app/Exports/PL/` if `QuotationExport` would bloat |

### Shared layer stay thin

Shared `Form.vue` / `Detail.vue` / `EndorsementService` / `QuotationExport`: **narrow branch only** (`isEndorsementRollout` / `isDirectBook` → call BUR slice). No drive-by PUL cleanup.

### Checklist before edit

- [ ] Change only for Direct Book / BUR?
- [ ] Would shared file diff be big or fragile? → **new BUR file**
- [ ] Shared touch = switch + delegate only?
- [ ] Claude Task used for implement (not Cursor solo)?
